## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="79128-104">クラスの読み取り/書き込みプロパティは、<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationAttribute> 属性でマークされます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79128-104">The read-write properties of a class are marked with the <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationAttribute> attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79128-105">また、各読み取り/書き込みプロパティは、<xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.Apply> または <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.OnCommit>の2種類のいずれかになります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79128-105">In addition, each read-write property can be one of two types: <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.Apply> or <xref:System.Management.Instrumentation.ManagementConfigurationType.OnCommit>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79128-106">クラスに OnCommit として構成されている読み取り/書き込みプロパティがある場合、クラスには ManagementCommit 属性でマークされたメソッドが必要です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79128-106">If a class has read-write properties that are configured as OnCommit, the class should have a method that is marked with the ManagementCommit attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79128-107">すべての OnCommit プロパティが設定されると、関連付けられたメソッドが呼び出されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79128-107">The associated method will be called when all OnCommit properties have been set.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="79128-108">マークされたメソッドはスレッドセーフではありません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79128-108">The marked method is not thread safe.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="79128-109">ManagementCommit 属性でマークされているメソッドがない場合、クラスは更新が完了したことを示すことなく、構成の更新を単独で管理します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79128-109">If no method is marked with the ManagementCommit attribute, the class manages the configuration updates by itself without any indication that the update has completed.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="79128-110">ManagementCommit 属性でマークされたメソッドは、パラメーターを取らず、戻り値の型が void です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79128-110">The method marked with the ManagementCommit attribute does not take any parameters and it has a void return type.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
public class Process  
{  
    /// Key attribute marks a key property. Keys are not changeable.  
    /// Keys have to be unique information.  
    [ManagementKey]  
    public int Id   
    {  
        get {    }  
    }  
  
    /// ManagementConfiguration stands for read/write manageable  
    /// property from a read/write field.  
    [ManagementConfiguration]  
    public string UserDefinedString;  
  
    [ManagementCommit]  
    void SaveOnDevice();  
}  
```
